gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 122, Spurs 119
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Spurs, 122-119. Anthony Davis recorded 37 points, 10 rebounds, and four steals for the Lakers, with Taurean Prince adding 17 points, five rebounds, and five assists in the victory. Victor Wembanyama tallied 30 points (4-5 3PM), 13 rebounds, and six blocks for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 15-10 in the regular season, while the Spurs fall 3-20.
